ultrawork.original_prompt:
@docs/test_logs/ has container logs from the first attempt to launch this in docker on a dev server. There are multiple issues in multiple containers.

Ralph ULW

Build a comprehensive list of the errors identified; then investigate all possible causes of the errors before diagnosing an issue; develop a comprehensive "fix" plan for all the issues and then allocate these to subagents.

On completion run a comprehensive code review and validation, update all documentation, commit, merge and push.
